search_results.title: About Eric Caron – Author of SWITCHED ON
search_results.snippet: Eric Caron is a retired U.S. Diplomat, U.S. Special Agent, HSBC Middle East Bank Executive and author of SWITCHED ON – The Heart and Mind of a Special Agent.

search_results.title: John E. Douglas
search_results.snippet: John Edward Douglas (born June 18, 1945) is an American retired special agent and unit chief in the United States Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI).
